README
========================================================================
EzChaff provides a simple way of adding chaff to a string in a
predictable manner and subsequently removing that chaff.

Usage

require 'rubygems'
gem 'ez_chaff','0.2'
require 'ez_chaff'
chaffed_string = EzChaff.chaff(string)
unchaffed_string = EzChaff.unchaff(string)
